<scenariocontexthint>
<![CDATA[
        In this Learning Scenario, you will see what is constitute as an application that is not eligble for loan! Given an application(which is considered complete),
        Its credit History Assessment done by Finance Officer, and Property Appraisal done by Property Appraiser, you as a Loan Officer
        need to decide if the given application is eligible for the Loan! 
        
        
     ]]>
</scenariocontexthint>

